# ODM

<p align="center">
    <em>MongoDB-ODM, NOSQL databases in Python, designed for simplicity, compatibility, and robustness.</em>
</p>

<p align="center">

<a href="https://github.com/nayan32biswas/mongodb-odm" target="_blank">
